= STARS Deployment README =

== Requirements ==

Python 2.6.*

== Release Process ==

http://code.aashedev.org/stars/wiki/ReleaseProcess

== Fabric ==

This project uses fabric to deploy code to dev, stage, and production environments

=== Example Deploy ===

>$ bin/fab dev deploy
You will be prompted to offer a specific revision/tag/branch, otherwise the latest trunk will be deployed

>$ bin/fab production deploy
Again, you are prompted, but this time for a tag name.